/tools/file-hash

A tool for hashing files on chain. 
Files are stored locally btu hashed on chain 
When a user drops a file into the hash pad, it will be hashed and the hash will be sent to the blockchain

User must pay for hashing
User can save the file to the blockchain
User can download the file from the blockchain
User can verify the file on chain
User can delete the file from the blockchain
User can update the file on chain
User can view the file on chain

User recieves receipt of hashed document 
Document is stamped and returned with visible timestamp and time and date of hash and signature of user 


